description:
I go here every morning ... 

I'm also not a coffee drinker anymore and switched to tea almost 6 months ago. 

@first-timers! 
I recommend the iced Mint Mojito or one of the hot coffees: Philtered Soul, Tesora, or Philharmonic. Philz drinks are customizable by size, cream, and sweetness. 

@tea-drinkers 
For a smooth drink that's kind of latte-y, 
I'd recommend their iced black tea (w/ or /o mint) sweet and lightly creamy with 2% since they default use heavy whipping cream I believe. 

@coffee-drinkers 
Popular coffee drinks seem to be philtered soul, tesora, and philharmonic. These are based on the coffees I hear being called out from 7-9 am :) 

@general
Love the employees, one barista remembers my order now after only two weeks of coming here and another told me she was going to make my drink because it sounded good. I love this place!

@people-who-rush-to-work
Use Order Ahead, the app and submit your order with absolute ease and reliability. I've used this app several times simply to try it out and every time, my drink is on the left end of the store right under the large sign "Order Ahead Pickup" exactly at the promised pick-up time. I've seen the soonest pickup time vary from 20-40 minutes. The cost is exactly the same as buying in person. 

@students/cafe-readers 
This place has a decent amount of seats where most are near some outlet. There are also great outdoor seats sprinkled all around the cafe.
